  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [X] Foundry\n- [X] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\nforge 0.2.0 (28312e7 2022-10-13T06:10:43.734727384Z)\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\nforge build\n\n### Operating System\n\nLinux\n\n### Describe the bug\n\nFoundry recompiles the whole contracts everytime even if there is no change to the code. Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\nclone [this repo's branch](https://github.com/aavegotchi/aavegotchi-realm-diamond/tree/cartridge_receipts-_and_discounts)\r\n\r\nrun `forge build`\r\n\r\nthen run `forge build` again\r\n\r\nit recompiles even though there is no change to the contracts",
